com.interpss.core.net

Interface Zone

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ZoneImpl

    public interface Zone
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Zone'. A name tagged element for the Loss Zone concept. A zone is optionally belong to an area.

    The following features are supported:

    • Network
    • Area
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getZone()
